WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:00:53.220 --> 00:00:54.346
Kitana...

3
00:00:54.430 --> 00:00:55.639
I have something for you.

4
00:00:56.766 --> 00:00:57.892
It will protect you.

5
00:00:59.769 --> 00:01:01.479
It's beautiful. Father.

6
00:01:03.481 --> 00:01:05.399
This was a gift from Lord Raiden.

7
00:01:05.483 --> 00:01:06.609
The God of Thunder.

8
00:01:08.194 --> 00:01:10.529
If anything were to happen to me.

9
00:01:10.613 --> 00:01:12.448
he's always listening.

10
00:01:19.789 --> 00:01:22.041
Shao Kahn is arriving. Your Majesty.

11
00:01:22.124 --> 00:01:24.293
What happens if you lose?

12
00:01:25.711 --> 00:01:27.004
Don't worry about that.

13
00:01:27.087 --> 00:01:28.964
But what if he's too strong?

14
00:01:29.048 --> 00:01:30.800
Strength is not a closed fist.

15
00:01:31.425 --> 00:01:32.718
Strength is here.

16
00:01:33.844 --> 00:01:34.844
and here.

17
00:01:38.182 --> 00:01:39.600
Be strong. Kitana.

18
00:01:46.816 --> 00:01:51.195
Jerrod. our king! Jerrod. our king!

19
00:02:06.293 --> 00:02:09.171
<i>Shao Kahn. Emperor of Outworld.</i>

20
00:02:09.255 --> 00:02:12.341
<i>sought to unite the various realms
under one rule.</i>

21
00:02:12.883 --> 00:02:13.883
<i>His.</i>

22
00:02:15.553 --> 00:02:18.722
<i>But the Elder Gods had put
certain precautions in place.</i>

23
00:02:21.684 --> 00:02:24.937
<i>Our fates would not be settled
by the size of our armies.</i>

24
00:02:27.189 --> 00:02:30.818
<i>They would be decided by combat.</i>

25
00:02:31.861 --> 00:02:33.320
<i>The rules were simple.</i>

26
00:02:34.113 --> 00:02:37.408
<i>If one realm could win
ten tournaments in a row.</i>

27
00:02:37.491 --> 00:02:40.119
<i>it would be given dominion over the other.</i>

28
00:02:40.786 --> 00:02:44.081
<i>Outworld would be allowed
to pillage Edenia's resources.</i>

29
00:02:45.583 --> 00:02:47.251
<i>Enslave our people.</i>

30
00:02:51.672 --> 00:02:55.217
<i>This was the final tournament.
Our last chance.</i>

31
00:02:56.135 --> 00:02:59.096
<i>All of our greatest
warriors had already fallen.</i>

32
00:03:00.681 --> 00:03:02.266
<i>Only one fighter remained.</i>

33
00:03:03.100 --> 00:03:04.268
<i>My father.</i>

34
00:03:05.895 --> 00:03:07.855
<i>King Jerrod of Edenia.</i>

35
00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:12.401
<i>But he faced Outworld's greatest warrior.</i>

36
00:03:14.612 --> 00:03:16.739
<i>Shao Kahn himself.</i>

37
00:03:27.166 --> 00:03:30.169
They will never bow to you.

38
00:03:31.337 --> 00:03:32.963
We shall see.

39
00:04:29.520 --> 00:04:30.521
Never!

40
00:05:26.285 --> 00:05:27.828
Kitana. close your eyes.

41
00:05:28.704 --> 00:05:30.539
Close your eyes right now.

42
00:05:44.261 --> 00:05:47.139
No!

43
00:05:47.222 --> 00:05:49.099
No!

44
00:05:51.518 --> 00:05:54.563
No!

45
00:06:25.344 --> 00:06:28.680
Edenia now belongs to me.

46
00:07:06.969 --> 00:07:09.888
Kneel. Or you'll die.

47
00:08:17.581 --> 00:08:20.042
Your father shouldn't
have brought you here.

48
00:08:31.762 --> 00:08:34.473
Kitana. you're my daughter now.

49
00:08:48.820 --> 00:08:49.905
Kitana!

50
00:09:26.692 --> 00:09:27.692
Yield.

51
00:09:47.462 --> 00:09:49.172
You cannot be serious.

52
00:09:49.881 --> 00:09:52.217
You're the one who taught me.
everything's a weapon.

53
00:10:00.851 --> 00:10:02.144
You yield.

54
00:10:16.575 --> 00:10:17.659
What do you have there?

55
00:10:18.243 --> 00:10:19.369
It's nothing.

56
00:10:21.121 --> 00:10:22.121
Jade.

57
00:10:24.374 --> 00:10:25.917
It was 20 years ago today

58
00:10:26.001 --> 00:10:28.003
the Emperor named me as your bodyguard.

59
00:10:29.338 --> 00:10:31.757
I know what Shao Kahn took from you.

60
00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:33.884
And if you had been vicious or cruel to me.

61
00:10:33.967 --> 00:10:35.260
no one would have blamed you.

62
00:10:35.344 --> 00:10:37.929
but you treated me like family.

63
00:10:39.014 --> 00:10:40.140
Like a sister.

64
00:10:42.267 --> 00:10:43.727
You are my sister.

65
00:10:44.728 --> 00:10:46.438
In every way that matters.

66
00:10:49.441 --> 00:10:53.111
Um. I got you something.
For the tournament.

67
00:10:58.075 --> 00:10:59.743
I was told that a proper princess

68
00:10:59.826 --> 00:11:02.871
is supposed to sit around
on pillows. fanning herself.

69
00:11:04.081 --> 00:11:05.165
Then I thought

70
00:11:05.874 --> 00:11:08.627
you are not exactly the pillow type.

71
00:11:13.215 --> 00:11:14.716
These are amazing.

72
00:11:27.813 --> 00:11:28.980
Hello. Mother.

73
00:11:30.232 --> 00:11:33.110
I was beginning to think
you were avoiding me.

74
00:11:33.735 --> 00:11:36.321
I've been busy.
Training for the tournament.

75
00:11:38.073 --> 00:11:40.117
Good.
Because I have petitioned

76
00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:42.202
the Elder Gods for the tournament to begin.

77
00:11:42.994 --> 00:11:45.539
Let Raiden scrounge
for his little champions.

78
00:11:46.081 --> 00:11:48.250
They will simply be the first to die

79
00:11:48.875 --> 00:11:50.168
and Earthrealm will be mine.

80
00:11:57.092 --> 00:11:58.218
Why is he here?

81
00:11:58.802 --> 00:12:00.846
I have a task for Shang Tsung.

82
00:12:02.180 --> 00:12:04.850
I hope you bring good news. Sorcerer.

83
00:12:04.933 --> 00:12:06.935
My spies have located the relic.

84
00:12:07.978 --> 00:12:09.938
It was last seen in Raiden's temple

85
00:12:10.021 --> 00:12:12.524
where it was stolen by the mercenary. Kano.

86
00:12:13.567 --> 00:12:15.277
We seek the Amulet of Shinnok.

87
00:12:16.236 --> 00:12:18.697
It is said the amulet can heal any wound.

88
00:12:18.780 --> 00:12:21.324
Transform a man into a god.

89
00:12:21.408 --> 00:12:22.951
To charge the amulet would require

90
00:12:23.034 --> 00:12:25.162
an impossible amount of power.

91
00:12:25.245 --> 00:12:27.831
We would need to capture
a star from the heavens.

92
00:12:27.914 --> 00:12:30.959
A star...

93
00:12:31.042 --> 00:12:32.377
or a god.

94
00:12:33.545 --> 00:12:35.797
Outworld has issued their challenge

95
00:12:35.881 --> 00:12:37.507
and the Elder Gods have spoken.

96
00:12:37.591 --> 00:12:41.178
When the sand is gone.
the first round will begin.

97
00:12:42.179 --> 00:12:44.055
Mortal Kombat is upon us

98
00:12:44.764 --> 00:12:48.101
and yet we are still short one champion.

99
00:13:42.364 --> 00:13:44.074
It's showtime.

100
00:14:24.072 --> 00:14:26.324
You should have brought more guys.

101
00:14:59.608 --> 00:15:01.484
Man. Johnny Cage got old as fuck.

102
00:15:07.532 --> 00:15:08.742
<i>Attention fans.</i>

103
00:15:08.825 --> 00:15:11.494
<i>don't miss your chance to meet
your favorite influencers</i>

104
00:15:11.578 --> 00:15:14.289
<i>and YouTube stars in Autograph Alley.</i>

105
00:15:14.372 --> 00:15:15.957
All right. everyone. get in close.

106
00:15:16.041 --> 00:15:17.125
Black Orchid!

107
00:15:27.260 --> 00:15:28.428
<i>It's showtime.</i>

108
00:15:44.444 --> 00:15:45.445
Johnny Cage.

109
00:15:46.279 --> 00:15:48.239
Hey. guys. I'm off the clock.

110
00:15:49.366 --> 00:15:52.869
Mr. Cage. you have been chosen
for Mortal Kombat.

111
00:15:52.952 --> 00:15:54.871
Mortal Kombat. huh?

112
00:15:54.954 --> 00:15:56.998
What's that? Some kind of fan film?

113
00:15:57.082 --> 00:15:58.917
It's a fighting tournament.

114
00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:01.586
Yeah. not really my thing anymore.

115
00:16:03.838 --> 00:16:05.048
Unless it's a paying gig?

116
00:16:05.590 --> 00:16:08.093
More like a "fate of the
entire human race" gig.

117
00:16:08.176 --> 00:16:10.470
Tell me you're not some crazy fans.

118
00:16:11.054 --> 00:16:12.347
Definitely not fans.

119
00:16:12.430 --> 00:16:13.430
All right. All right.

120
00:16:13.473 --> 00:16:14.784
You don't have to say "definitely."

121
00:16:14.808 --> 00:16:15.809
You have been chosen

122
00:16:15.892 --> 00:16:17.644
as one of the champions of Earthrealm.

123
00:16:18.395 --> 00:16:21.064
The gods have selected you. Mr. Cage.

124
00:16:21.940 --> 00:16:24.442
All right. I think it's time
for you guys to fuck off.

125
00:16:24.526 --> 00:16:26.653
But. hey. love the cosplay. What's that?

126
00:16:26.736 --> 00:16:28.947
<i>Big Trouble in Little China?</i>
Fantastic film.

127
00:16:29.030 --> 00:16:30.383
Listen. I know what it sounds like.

128
00:16:30.407 --> 00:16:31.866
but he's telling the truth.

129
00:16:31.950 --> 00:16:35.120
Very soon the champions
will be summoned to fight

130
00:16:35.203 --> 00:16:36.621
and you will be among them.

131
00:16:36.705 --> 00:16:38.331
The fate of your world

132
00:16:38.415 --> 00:16:40.291
rests on the outcome of this tournament.

133
00:16:41.042 --> 00:16:43.586
Fantastic. I will see you there.

134
00:16:43.670 --> 00:16:45.463
Thanks for coming. drive safe.

135
00:16:45.547 --> 00:16:47.549
and. uh. say hi to Dumbledore for me.

136
00:16:47.632 --> 00:16:49.175
You're gonna have to show him.

137
00:17:03.815 --> 00:17:05.275
Holy shit.

138
00:17:06.025 --> 00:17:07.485
How are you doing that?

139
00:17:07.569 --> 00:17:09.320
Come with us. Mr. Cage.

140
00:17:09.404 --> 00:17:12.031
and discover the man you were meant to be.

141
00:17:18.621 --> 00:17:20.206
Now. are you coming or what?

142
00:17:45.774 --> 00:17:46.983
Where the hell am I?

143
00:17:48.777 --> 00:17:50.695
It's okay.
You're still on Earth.

144
00:17:50.779 --> 00:17:52.489
Welcome to Raiden's Sky Temple.

145
00:17:59.078 --> 00:18:00.747
Watch this.

146
00:18:02.248 --> 00:18:05.043
Robot arms. That dude's got robot arms.

147
00:18:06.503 --> 00:18:07.962
We served in the Army together.

148
00:18:08.046 --> 00:18:09.839
That's Jax Briggs. Special Forces.

149
00:18:11.341 --> 00:18:12.550
That's Cole Young.

150
00:18:12.634 --> 00:18:14.928
His suit absorbs attacks
and makes him stronger.

151
00:18:15.887 --> 00:18:17.388
He's a descendant of Scorpion.

152
00:18:17.472 --> 00:18:19.432
One of Earthrealm's greatest warriors.

153
00:18:20.517 --> 00:18:21.559
Oh.

154
00:18:21.643 --> 00:18:22.769
That's Liu Kang.

155
00:18:23.603 --> 00:18:25.230
He's the best fighter we got.

156
00:18:33.613 --> 00:18:35.949
- He shoots fire?
- Mm-hmm.

157
00:18:37.992 --> 00:18:40.453
I feel like that's cheating. but okay.

158
00:18:41.663 --> 00:18:42.848
It kind of feels like bullshit

159
00:18:42.872 --> 00:18:44.541
that y'all have these crazy powers

160
00:18:44.624 --> 00:18:46.793
and I'm just. you know.
incredibly handsome.

161
00:18:48.086 --> 00:18:49.420
It could take months of training

162
00:18:49.504 --> 00:18:50.630
to unlock your powers.

163
00:18:51.339 --> 00:18:52.619
We don't have that kind of time.

164
00:18:52.674 --> 00:18:54.050
Yeah. well. whose fault is that?

165
00:18:54.133 --> 00:18:55.486
I mean. if you knew this was coming.

166
00:18:55.510 --> 00:18:57.238
why'd you wait till the
last second to find me?

167
00:18:57.262 --> 00:18:59.973
We used to have
another champion. Kung Lao.

168
00:19:00.056 --> 00:19:01.641
Oh. great. so I'm just the fucking sub.

169
00:19:01.724 --> 00:19:03.852
He was murdered. By Shang Tsung.

170
00:19:03.935 --> 00:19:06.104
Wait. Murdered?

171
00:19:07.856 --> 00:19:10.066
Come on. You can't be serious. Right?

172
00:19:10.608 --> 00:19:12.861
I mean. that's. like.
gotta be against the rules.

173
00:19:13.361 --> 00:19:15.321
You can't just go around killing people.

174
00:19:16.781 --> 00:19:19.284
It's called Mortal Kombat for a reason.

175
00:19:20.410 --> 00:19:23.788
Yo. Gandalf. send me back.
I wanna go back.

176
00:19:23.872 --> 00:19:26.165
- Johnny. wait.
- No. No.

177
00:19:26.249 --> 00:19:28.001
You said tournament which implies rules.

178
00:19:28.084 --> 00:19:30.169
and a referee. and I don't
know. maybe a medic.

179
00:19:30.253 --> 00:19:32.297
Not some fucking <i>Squid Game</i> murder party.

180
00:19:32.380 --> 00:19:34.507
Dude wants to quit. just let him go.

181
00:19:34.591 --> 00:19:35.592
We don't need him.

182
00:19:35.675 --> 00:19:38.803
Look. you wanna step in the octagon

183
00:19:38.887 --> 00:19:40.430
with a bunch of happy assholes

184
00:19:40.513 --> 00:19:43.474
that don't know how
to lose. go right ahead.

185
00:19:43.558 --> 00:19:46.185
But I don't have Transformer arms.

186
00:19:46.269 --> 00:19:48.855
or shoot lightning bolts or fireballs.

187
00:19:48.938 --> 00:19:51.399
or do whatever the fuck
it is Flame Fingers does.

188
00:19:51.482 --> 00:19:54.319
so forgive me if I don't
sign up to get mulched.

189
00:19:58.281 --> 00:20:00.199
You are not wrong. Mr. Cage.

190
00:20:08.541 --> 00:20:10.293
Nine times. we have been challenged.

191
00:20:10.376 --> 00:20:12.170
And nine times. we have lost.

192
00:20:12.253 --> 00:20:14.047
And now. 20 years later.

193
00:20:14.130 --> 00:20:17.091
Shao Kahn seeks to add
Earthrealm to his dominion.

194
00:20:18.259 --> 00:20:21.054
This is a war for the fate of your world.

195
00:20:22.221 --> 00:20:25.016
Look. Cage. I get it. We all do.

196
00:20:25.099 --> 00:20:27.143
Some stupid fucking cosmic lottery

197
00:20:27.226 --> 00:20:29.896
decided that we're the ones
that get to save the world.

198
00:20:32.649 --> 00:20:34.192
Shit is terrifying.

199
00:20:34.817 --> 00:20:35.878
You wanna know the last thing I did

200
00:20:35.902 --> 00:20:36.903
before coming here?

201
00:20:36.986 --> 00:20:40.365
I said goodbye to my
wife and my little girl.

202
00:20:40.448 --> 00:20:43.618
The two most important things in my life.

203
00:20:43.701 --> 00:20:45.078
And there's a damn good chance

204
00:20:45.161 --> 00:20:46.579
I'm never gonna see them again.

205
00:20:48.414 --> 00:20:49.457
And I'm okay with that.

206
00:20:50.875 --> 00:20:53.711
Because I know if I die out there.
I'm dying for them.

207
00:20:55.129 --> 00:20:57.840
We lose one more time. the Earth is gone.

208
00:20:57.924 --> 00:21:00.426
And our only chance
is to face this together.

209
00:21:01.010 --> 00:21:05.390
You. Johnny Cage. are a part of this now.

210
00:21:14.357 --> 00:21:15.525
Fuck that.

211
00:21:15.608 --> 00:21:17.193
Johnny. even if you walk away.

212
00:21:17.276 --> 00:21:19.076
the Elder Gods can still
summon you to fight.

213
00:21:19.112 --> 00:21:20.196
Not if they can't find me.

214
00:21:20.279 --> 00:21:21.948
So what are you gonna do. huh?

215
00:21:22.031 --> 00:21:23.408
You just going to go hide?

216
00:21:23.491 --> 00:21:25.535
No. first I'm gonna drink
every beer on the planet.

217
00:21:25.618 --> 00:21:26.703
then I'm going to hide.

218
00:21:26.786 --> 00:21:28.597
Because this shit's got
nothing to do with me.

219
00:21:28.621 --> 00:21:30.623
I'm not some great warrior.

220
00:21:30.707 --> 00:21:32.208
I'm not some champion.

221
00:21:32.291 --> 00:21:34.335
Okay? I'm an actor.

222
00:21:34.419 --> 00:21:35.420
Hmm.

223
00:21:36.713 --> 00:21:38.033
And before that. you were the guy

224
00:21:38.089 --> 00:21:40.299
with five black belts and a world title.

225
00:21:42.301 --> 00:21:45.054
Yeah. I saw some of those old fights.

226
00:21:46.139 --> 00:21:49.350
Man. you could have been one of the best.

227
00:21:49.434 --> 00:21:52.228
But I wasn't.
And that was a long time ago.

228
00:21:52.311 --> 00:21:55.106
That guy you want is dead and buried.

229
00:21:56.107 --> 00:21:58.359
Or maybe he's still in
there. trying to get out.

230
00:22:18.921 --> 00:22:19.922
Hey. listen...

231
00:22:22.008 --> 00:22:24.177
I'm like 90% sure I had an aneurysm

232
00:22:24.260 --> 00:22:26.596
and this is some kind of
fucked up coma dream.

233
00:22:28.765 --> 00:22:30.600
but on the off chance this shit is real.

234
00:22:32.310 --> 00:22:34.353
best of luck with the whole
saving the world thing.

235
00:22:49.952 --> 00:22:53.122
You should know that when you died.

236
00:22:53.206 --> 00:22:57.543
it was not your so-called friends
who brought you back.

237
00:22:58.711 --> 00:23:00.922
It was not Lord Raiden.

238
00:23:01.714 --> 00:23:03.591
the Great Pretender.

239
00:23:05.551 --> 00:23:07.595
It was Shao Kahn.

240
00:23:09.013 --> 00:23:10.681
Rise now.

241
00:23:11.557 --> 00:23:15.186
as a champion of Outworld.

242
00:23:21.818 --> 00:23:25.113
Sire. we retrieved the package.

243
00:23:27.532 --> 00:23:28.533
Quan Chi!

244
00:23:29.367 --> 00:23:31.828
I am told you sent your
followers to Earthrealm.

245
00:23:31.911 --> 00:23:33.079
What were they doing there?

246
00:23:33.162 --> 00:23:36.082
Simply retrieving some
lost property. my lady.

247
00:23:36.958 --> 00:23:38.751
By order of your father.

248
00:23:41.379 --> 00:23:42.380
What is that?

249
00:23:47.009 --> 00:23:48.803
I believe it's called...

250
00:23:49.720 --> 00:23:50.930
a "Kano."

251
00:23:55.977 --> 00:23:57.687
One Sling Dog please.

252
00:24:03.484 --> 00:24:04.652
You're Johnny Cage.

253
00:24:05.778 --> 00:24:07.446
That's what the tab says.

254
00:24:07.530 --> 00:24:09.073
Holy shit.

255
00:24:09.615 --> 00:24:13.077
I freaking loved <i>Citizen
Cage</i> when I was a kid.

256
00:24:14.954 --> 00:24:16.539
Thanks. man. I appreciate it.

257
00:24:18.583 --> 00:24:20.001
Dude. you know what they should do?

258
00:24:21.294 --> 00:24:23.337
They should do another <i>Citizen Cage.</i>

259
00:24:23.421 --> 00:24:24.839
Like a reboot.

260
00:24:25.840 --> 00:24:27.758
Come on. man. Give me a break.

261
00:24:28.384 --> 00:24:29.384
Nobody wants that.

262
00:24:30.052 --> 00:24:30.887
What?

263
00:24:30.970 --> 00:24:32.197
You think the world is crying out

264
00:24:32.221 --> 00:24:35.266
for a Johnny Cage comeback? Huh?

265
00:24:36.184 --> 00:24:38.603
No. They want gritty.
they want grounded.

266
00:24:38.686 --> 00:24:39.604
they want Keanu Reeves

267
00:24:39.687 --> 00:24:41.856
murdering a thousand
fucking dudes with a pencil.

268
00:24:41.939 --> 00:24:43.774
That's what people wanna see.

269
00:24:45.693 --> 00:24:49.488
Not some dinosaur doing
a bunch of karate poses.

270
00:24:50.781 --> 00:24:52.533
That shit went out in the '90s.

271
00:24:56.662 --> 00:24:58.122
I thought it was pretty cool.

272
00:25:43.626 --> 00:25:45.378
Where's my fucking eye?

273
00:25:49.507 --> 00:25:50.591
Blondie.

274
00:25:52.009 --> 00:25:53.427
The tournament has begun.

275
00:25:54.428 --> 00:25:56.097
Today you fight for Earthrealm.

276
00:25:56.180 --> 00:25:58.266
For the lives of everyone
you have ever known.

277
00:25:58.349 --> 00:26:01.644
If you fail. the Earth fails with you.

278
00:26:02.353 --> 00:26:05.314
Two of our champions
will be chosen to compete today.

279
00:26:05.982 --> 00:26:06.983
The winners will advance

280
00:26:07.066 --> 00:26:08.776
to the next stage of the tournament.

281
00:26:09.402 --> 00:26:11.779
The losers will be eliminated.

282
00:26:11.862 --> 00:26:13.322
To the death.

283
00:26:13.406 --> 00:26:15.199
That is up to the winner.

284
00:26:16.158 --> 00:26:17.201
Maybe don't lose.

285
00:26:23.124 --> 00:26:25.293
Well. looks like it's my lucky day.

286
00:26:25.376 --> 00:26:27.420
Blade. you got this.

287
00:26:33.676 --> 00:26:35.511
I thought you said two of us were fighting.

288
00:26:40.266 --> 00:26:43.853
<i>It's Johnny Cage
with a brutal hit. He's down.</i>

289
00:26:43.936 --> 00:26:45.855
<i>It's official.</i>

290
00:26:45.938 --> 00:26:48.566
<i>Johnny Cage just became the youngest minor</i>

291
00:26:48.649 --> 00:26:50.192
<i>to ever win this tournament.</i>

292
00:26:50.276 --> 00:26:52.778
<i>This young man is destined for greatness.</i>

293
00:26:56.741 --> 00:26:58.284
You seem a little down. Johnny.

294
00:26:59.410 --> 00:27:01.245
You're normally a little more animated.

295
00:27:08.169 --> 00:27:09.587
<i>Uno más.</i> thanks. Ed.

296
00:27:29.982 --> 00:27:31.275
Oh. shit.

297
00:27:37.281 --> 00:27:38.508
I don't know what you're on about.

298
00:27:38.532 --> 00:27:39.658
The amulet of what now?

299
00:27:39.742 --> 00:27:41.619
Shinnok. Pay attention!

300
00:27:41.702 --> 00:27:43.342
Don't look at me with that tone of voice.

301
00:27:43.371 --> 00:27:44.747
you big bleached dildo.

302
00:27:44.830 --> 00:27:47.583
I've just been dead.
And my fucking eye's AWOL.

303
00:27:47.666 --> 00:27:50.878
Stop your incessant whinging.
We can build you another.

304
00:27:50.961 --> 00:27:53.005
Why is he not a Revenant
like the rest of them?

305
00:27:53.089 --> 00:27:55.424
He was not worth the time or the effort.

306
00:27:55.508 --> 00:27:58.135
This one barely has a soul left to corrupt.

307
00:27:58.219 --> 00:28:00.554
Ha! You hear that? A fucking loophole.

308
00:28:00.638 --> 00:28:01.972
Go. you good thing.

309
00:28:02.056 --> 00:28:05.226
Where is the amulet you took
from Raiden's temple?

310
00:28:05.309 --> 00:28:06.811
I don't know. probably in my pocket

311
00:28:06.894 --> 00:28:08.254
where I keep all the shit I steal.

312
00:28:09.939 --> 00:28:11.607
Oh. right-oh.

313
00:28:14.026 --> 00:28:17.405
Here we go. How about...

314
00:28:18.072 --> 00:28:20.032
Nah. different temple. Well. hold on.

315
00:28:20.950 --> 00:28:21.992
This could be...

316
00:28:22.493 --> 00:28:24.412
Yeah. Should call her.

317
00:28:25.371 --> 00:28:28.416
Ah! Here we are. Yahtzee.

318
00:28:29.041 --> 00:28:30.041
Oi!

319
00:28:30.084 --> 00:28:31.293
We could have left him dead.

320
00:28:31.377 --> 00:28:33.129
Hey! First off. fuck off.

321
00:28:33.212 --> 00:28:35.047
And you. where are you going with that?

322
00:28:36.298 --> 00:28:37.925
I will take it to my father.

323
00:28:39.260 --> 00:28:40.636
Unfortunately. Princess.

324
00:28:40.719 --> 00:28:43.055
it appears you are needed elsewhere.

325
00:28:45.391 --> 00:28:46.976
Oi. you creepy fucking mime.

326
00:28:47.059 --> 00:28:48.936
I stole that fair and square.

327
00:28:50.312 --> 00:28:51.689
Good luck.

328
00:29:12.418 --> 00:29:14.295
Each flame represents a fighter.

329
00:29:15.087 --> 00:29:16.589
The tournament ends when one side

330
00:29:16.672 --> 00:29:18.174
has no champions left.

331
00:29:19.049 --> 00:29:21.010
Hey. How's it going. babe?

332
00:29:22.928 --> 00:29:25.347
Listen. I'm warning you.

333
00:29:26.348 --> 00:29:29.310
I got a Saturn Award
for best fight in a feature film.

334
00:29:29.393 --> 00:29:30.644
so don't mess with me.

335
00:29:34.773 --> 00:29:37.318
Whoa! Whoa. Easy. all right?

336
00:29:37.401 --> 00:29:39.737
Let's just take a timeout
here and talk about it.

337
00:29:39.820 --> 00:29:42.573
Okay? I really don't feel
comfortable hitting a girl.

338
00:29:44.116 --> 00:29:46.410
Don't worry. you won't.

339
00:29:57.963 --> 00:29:59.843
Whoa! Come on. Easy.
Let's just talk about this.

340
00:30:22.780 --> 00:30:24.240
Why are you so fucking mean?

341
00:32:16.560 --> 00:32:18.228
Finish him!

342
00:32:32.576 --> 00:32:33.577
Hmm.

343
00:32:57.768 --> 00:33:00.354
It appears your side is already down a man.

344
00:33:01.563 --> 00:33:02.606
Tragic.

345
00:33:05.567 --> 00:33:06.610
And who are you?

346
00:33:07.111 --> 00:33:09.738
Sindel. High Queen of Edenia.

347
00:33:09.822 --> 00:33:12.116
Consort to the great Shao Kahn.

348
00:33:12.199 --> 00:33:14.118
They send their queen to fight?

349
00:33:14.618 --> 00:33:17.830
No. We send our best to fight.

350
00:33:17.913 --> 00:33:18.913
Oh.

351
00:33:19.581 --> 00:33:22.042
No offense. babe.
but you look really fucking dead.

352
00:33:22.126 --> 00:33:24.336
I was freed from my mortal bonds.

353
00:33:24.420 --> 00:33:25.546
Shao Kahn showed me

354
00:33:25.629 --> 00:33:27.297
the pleasures of a life eternal.

355
00:33:31.969 --> 00:33:33.887
Perhaps I'll do the same for you.

356
00:33:43.772 --> 00:33:45.065
What a pretty trick.

357
00:33:46.150 --> 00:33:47.693
Would you like to see mine?

358
00:33:48.569 --> 00:33:50.195
No. actually I'm good.

359
00:34:13.302 --> 00:34:15.679
Fuck you! You stupid bitch!

360
00:35:22.621 --> 00:35:24.498
It appears our sides are now even.

361
00:35:30.087 --> 00:35:31.296
What'd I miss?

362
00:35:32.005 --> 00:35:34.132
Fuck yeah! Look who's back.

363
00:35:36.093 --> 00:35:37.928
Well? How bad was it?

364
00:35:38.011 --> 00:35:41.723
Zombie queen. Pit of spikes. Yeah.

365
00:35:41.807 --> 00:35:43.308
- So pretty goddamn bad.
- Ow.

366
00:35:45.435 --> 00:35:46.645
- You okay?
- Yeah.

367
00:35:50.941 --> 00:35:52.067
What happened?

368
00:35:52.150 --> 00:35:54.444
You were eliminated from the tournament.

369
00:35:55.571 --> 00:35:56.655
You lost.

370
00:35:56.738 --> 00:35:59.533
You are lucky. she was charitable
and let you live.

371
00:36:07.457 --> 00:36:09.209
Oi! Pennywise.

372
00:36:09.293 --> 00:36:11.503
I've been looking all
over this shithole for you.

373
00:36:11.587 --> 00:36:13.130
You promised me a new eye.

374
00:36:13.213 --> 00:36:14.840
And it better be one that shoots lasers.

375
00:36:15.382 --> 00:36:18.385
- I have other priorities.
- Like fucking what?

376
00:36:18.468 --> 00:36:19.928
If it's putting on more eyeliner.

377
00:36:20.012 --> 00:36:21.471
trust me. you're good.

378
00:36:21.555 --> 00:36:22.848
All right? Come on. mate.

379
00:36:22.931 --> 00:36:25.392
I am bumping into shit
left. right. and center.

380
00:36:25.475 --> 00:36:27.185
I mean. my peripheral vision is fucked.

381
00:36:27.269 --> 00:36:29.021
Proper fucked. mate.

382
00:36:29.104 --> 00:36:31.023
So come on. Chop-chop. Let's get to it.

383
00:36:32.774 --> 00:36:34.210
Well. you don't have to do it right now.

384
00:36:34.234 --> 00:36:36.945
I mean. you need to.
you know. take a measurement.

385
00:36:37.029 --> 00:36:40.282
Check the color or wash
your grubby little hands.

386
00:36:43.577 --> 00:36:44.953
All right. let's have a look.

387
00:36:45.037 --> 00:36:47.956
Don't fucking roll it on
the fucking ground. you grub!

388
00:36:49.416 --> 00:36:51.126
Oi. the amulet.

389
00:36:51.793 --> 00:36:54.379
I want that back.
And don't fucking roll it.

390
00:36:54.463 --> 00:36:57.174
You got your eye.
Now leave me alone.

391
00:36:57.257 --> 00:36:59.426
The amulet does not belong to you.

392
00:36:59.968 --> 00:37:01.845
Its powers are well beyond

393
00:37:01.929 --> 00:37:03.722
your meager understanding.

394
00:37:03.805 --> 00:37:04.806
Idiot.

395
00:37:04.890 --> 00:37:07.100
All right. Let's take
this baby for a test drive.

396
00:37:07.851 --> 00:37:09.937
All right.

397
00:37:11.063 --> 00:37:15.317
One. two. three. Oh! Fuck! Snug.

398
00:37:18.695 --> 00:37:20.697
Wow.

399
00:37:20.781 --> 00:37:23.116
Holy shit. is that HD?
That's pretty good.

400
00:37:23.200 --> 00:37:25.452
How many eyes you made?
Can you do me other one?

401
00:37:38.799 --> 00:37:40.634
You seem troubled. Mr. Cage.

402
00:37:42.469 --> 00:37:44.596
Yeah. Well. 'cause of me

403
00:37:44.680 --> 00:37:47.015
Earth's odds just got 20% worse.

404
00:37:47.724 --> 00:37:49.935
I had a chance to actually
do something worth a damn

405
00:37:50.018 --> 00:37:51.603
and I screwed it all up.

406
00:37:51.687 --> 00:37:55.774
So. yeah. I'd say "troubled"
just about sums it up.

407
00:38:04.032 --> 00:38:07.077
What are those? Pills?

408
00:38:07.160 --> 00:38:08.495
Huh?

409
00:38:09.454 --> 00:38:10.872
Are they magic fighting pills?

410
00:38:11.957 --> 00:38:14.167
Is that...
Is that how you get your powers?

411
00:38:23.552 --> 00:38:24.636
Bird seed.

412
00:38:26.263 --> 00:38:29.349
Oh. Yeah. yeah. yeah. Bird seed. Yeah.

413
00:38:30.642 --> 00:38:34.062
Well. I thought you were gonna
give me some kind of lecture.

414
00:38:34.146 --> 00:38:37.649
but yeah. chores are good.

415
00:38:40.527 --> 00:38:42.070
You don't need a lecture.

416
00:38:42.154 --> 00:38:43.864
You need perspective.

417
00:38:43.947 --> 00:38:46.616
Perspective. huh?

418
00:38:46.700 --> 00:38:48.952
There are eight billion
people on this planet

419
00:38:49.036 --> 00:38:51.163
and yet the gods chose you.

420
00:38:51.246 --> 00:38:53.248
Perhaps they saw your true potential

421
00:38:53.331 --> 00:38:54.916
as a champion of Earthrealm.

422
00:38:55.792 --> 00:38:57.335
Maybe they made a mistake.

423
00:38:57.419 --> 00:38:58.419
Maybe.

424
00:38:58.795 --> 00:39:01.923
If I see the Elder Gods.
I'll be sure to tell them.

425
00:39:06.678 --> 00:39:08.805
Well. I'm glad you
find this all so amusing.

426
00:39:10.057 --> 00:39:13.560
Hey. great pep talk. by the way.
Just nailed it.

427
00:39:59.523 --> 00:40:00.524
Ouch.

428
00:40:01.983 --> 00:40:03.568
You have done this before?

429
00:40:04.569 --> 00:40:05.821
I've seen it done.

430
00:40:07.823 --> 00:40:09.157
All right.

431
00:40:14.287 --> 00:40:17.916
It's okay. The Princess Kitana
has been my eyes and ears

432
00:40:17.999 --> 00:40:19.960
inside the palace for many years now.

433
00:40:21.795 --> 00:40:23.755
We know the risk you took coming here.

434
00:40:23.839 --> 00:40:25.006
Thank you. Kitana.

435
00:40:25.090 --> 00:40:27.342
Wait. are you telling
me I got my ass kicked

436
00:40:27.425 --> 00:40:28.593
by one of the good guys?

437
00:40:28.677 --> 00:40:31.388
I had to make it look real.
He was watching.

438
00:40:32.556 --> 00:40:34.641
They found the Amulet of Shinnok.

439
00:40:34.724 --> 00:40:35.725
It was in the possession

440
00:40:35.809 --> 00:40:37.310
of a dead sellsword named Kano.

441
00:40:37.894 --> 00:40:39.521
Son of a bitch.

442
00:40:39.604 --> 00:40:41.332
If the Emperor finds a
way to charge the amulet.

443
00:40:41.356 --> 00:40:42.941
he would be unstoppable.

444
00:40:43.024 --> 00:40:44.734
It would be like fighting a god.

445
00:40:44.818 --> 00:40:47.279
Yeah. well. let's not do that.

446
00:40:48.071 --> 00:40:49.739
My friend is in the tournament.

447
00:40:50.991 --> 00:40:52.551
Jade was raised under Shao Kahn's army.

448
00:40:53.577 --> 00:40:57.455
Do what you must. but
do not make her suffer.

449
00:41:09.759 --> 00:41:11.469
You went to another realm?

450
00:41:14.055 --> 00:41:15.557
You followed me?

451
00:41:15.640 --> 00:41:17.851
I am trying to keep you alive.

452
00:41:17.934 --> 00:41:18.935
By spying on your friend.

453
00:41:19.019 --> 00:41:21.646
By keeping my friend from making a mistake.

454
00:41:21.730 --> 00:41:24.733
You are conspiring
with Lord Raiden. The enemy.

455
00:41:25.442 --> 00:41:27.527
I swore an oath. Kitana.

456
00:41:28.361 --> 00:41:31.865
To serve as Shao Kahn's sword.

457
00:41:39.497 --> 00:41:41.333
The second round of the tournament

458
00:41:41.416 --> 00:41:42.918
will consist of three matches.

459
00:41:43.793 --> 00:41:46.630
Jax. Cole. Liu Kang.

460
00:42:03.980 --> 00:42:05.148
Kung Lao.

461
00:42:06.566 --> 00:42:08.276
I have been given new life.

462
00:42:09.527 --> 00:42:10.779
My son?

463
00:42:20.038 --> 00:42:23.500
Look at that.
Still part of this tournament.

464
00:42:23.583 --> 00:42:25.335
But that's not why I'm here.

465
00:42:34.261 --> 00:42:36.221
No!

466
00:42:36.304 --> 00:42:37.430
No!

467
00:42:49.067 --> 00:42:50.360
Attack now!

468
00:43:28.732 --> 00:43:33.486
Imagine what one could do with such power.

469
00:43:35.113 --> 00:43:39.451
Careful. Sorcerer. that
doesn't belong to you.

470
00:43:47.042 --> 00:43:50.086
The amulet must be bound to a mortal soul.

471
00:43:50.170 --> 00:43:52.047
Once it has imprinted on you.

472
00:43:52.130 --> 00:43:54.090
Raiden's power will be yours.

473
00:43:54.674 --> 00:43:57.052
The amulet will give you immortality.

474
00:45:00.949 --> 00:45:04.285
Well. this is fucking ominous.

475
00:45:11.292 --> 00:45:13.086
I'm guessing you're Jade.

476
00:45:13.169 --> 00:45:15.004
Let's get this over with.

477
00:45:20.385 --> 00:45:23.221
I am told you carry the blood of Scorpion.

478
00:45:27.475 --> 00:45:29.269
I look forward to spilling it.

479
00:45:44.159 --> 00:45:46.119
You know you're fighting
on the wrong side. right?

480
00:45:57.130 --> 00:45:58.756
What the fuck do you have under there?

481
00:46:00.008 --> 00:46:01.634
Shit.

482
00:46:22.071 --> 00:46:23.071
Well. hello there.

483
00:46:31.789 --> 00:46:34.125
I hope your ancestors are watching.

484
00:47:05.949 --> 00:47:09.118
For what it is worth.
I take no joy in this.

485
00:47:12.038 --> 00:47:14.040
Then you're really going to hate this shit.

486
00:47:19.420 --> 00:47:20.838
This is for my family.

487
00:47:22.090 --> 00:47:23.091
For my friends.

488
00:47:24.259 --> 00:47:25.779
For every moment that brought me here.

489
00:47:27.095 --> 00:47:30.473
This is for Earth. you son of a bitch.

490
00:48:19.063 --> 00:48:20.063
What?

491
00:48:44.922 --> 00:48:46.716
Give my regards to the dead.

492
00:48:55.808 --> 00:48:58.436
Go on. do it.

493
00:49:22.126 --> 00:49:23.127
Why?

494
00:49:24.087 --> 00:49:25.755
Your friend spared one of our guys.

495
00:49:27.173 --> 00:49:28.173
Now we're even.

496
00:49:29.050 --> 00:49:31.761
By the way. hell of a fight.

497
00:49:54.575 --> 00:49:57.537
Kung Lao. what have they done to you?

498
00:49:58.121 --> 00:49:59.997
Opened my eyes to the truth.

499
00:50:02.959 --> 00:50:03.960
What truth?

500
00:50:04.585 --> 00:50:08.589
Look around. The gods have
abandoned their creation.

501
00:50:09.507 --> 00:50:11.843
Only Shao Kahn can save us now.

502
00:50:12.802 --> 00:50:16.013
One of those gods raised you. Loved you.

503
00:50:17.432 --> 00:50:18.891
And you slit his throat.

504
00:51:24.791 --> 00:51:28.419
Stop. Kung Lao. remember who you are!

505
00:51:30.296 --> 00:51:31.881
You were my brother.

506
00:51:31.964 --> 00:51:34.675
And when you're dead.
when your realm falls.

507
00:51:35.384 --> 00:51:37.220
we will be brothers again.

508
00:52:02.787 --> 00:52:04.205
Don't make me do this.

509
00:53:25.578 --> 00:53:27.038
I'll find a way to save you.

510
00:53:40.426 --> 00:53:42.345
I'm going to bring you back.

511
00:54:18.047 --> 00:54:21.008
But not today. brother.

512
00:54:40.861 --> 00:54:42.571
Raiden!

513
00:54:47.451 --> 00:54:50.621
- Is he?
- He's alive. Barely.

514
00:54:56.377 --> 00:54:57.837
He's been asking for you.

515
00:55:00.006 --> 00:55:01.007
Liu Kang.

516
00:55:08.055 --> 00:55:09.098
My son.

517
00:55:19.525 --> 00:55:20.526
What happened?

518
00:55:23.237 --> 00:55:24.280
I killed him.

519
00:55:25.573 --> 00:55:26.782
I didn't have a choice.

520
00:55:27.616 --> 00:55:28.617
I'm sorry.

521
00:55:33.205 --> 00:55:34.248
Where's Cole?

522
00:55:36.625 --> 00:55:37.835
He didn't come back?

523
00:55:41.047 --> 00:55:42.673
Oh. shit.

524
00:55:54.643 --> 00:55:55.895
Necromancer.

525
00:55:56.937 --> 00:55:59.190
give me your greatest warrior.

526
00:56:00.608 --> 00:56:02.610
The one they call Sub-Zero.

527
00:56:05.071 --> 00:56:07.073
<i>Bi-Han.</i>

