01:21:39.854 --> 01:21:40.938
Or is it Bi-Han.

800
01:21:41.814 --> 01:21:44.191
No. I think it's Bi-Han.
That Sub-Zero fucker.

801
01:21:44.275 --> 01:21:46.736
You know. he killed your
whole family or some shit.

802
01:21:46.819 --> 01:21:48.255
I mean. they tried to explain to me.

803
01:21:48.279 --> 01:21:50.239
but to be honest. I
wasn't really listening.

804
01:22:38.120 --> 01:22:41.749
I am Hanzo Hasashi of the Shirai Ryu

805
01:22:42.667 --> 01:22:45.878
and Hell bends to my command.

806
01:22:54.637 --> 01:22:56.097
Keeping the seat warm?

807
01:22:56.180 --> 01:22:59.183
Raiden has sent his last
warriors to Netherrealm.

808
01:22:59.684 --> 01:23:01.435
They are going after the amulet.

809
01:23:02.395 --> 01:23:04.522
That means there's no one left
to guard Lord Raiden.

810
01:23:09.151 --> 01:23:11.362
If we lose that amulet. we lose everything.

811
01:23:12.655 --> 01:23:14.573
Shao Kahn will be stripped of power.

812
01:23:15.199 --> 01:23:16.701
And our empire would fall.

813
01:23:16.784 --> 01:23:18.160
Send me down there.

814
01:23:18.869 --> 01:23:21.497
I will protect the amulet
while you take care of Raiden.

815
01:23:21.580 --> 01:23:24.291
I would think your loyalties
would be with your princess.

816
01:23:24.375 --> 01:23:25.835
Kitana made her choice.

817
01:23:27.545 --> 01:23:28.796
I'm making mine.

818
01:23:51.277 --> 01:23:53.696
How the hell are we going to
find the amulet in this place?

819
01:23:57.867 --> 01:23:59.535
Bi-Han is here.

820
01:24:06.459 --> 01:24:08.169
Hanzo Hasashi.

821
01:24:09.086 --> 01:24:11.797
this is not your fight. old man.

822
01:24:11.881 --> 01:24:14.550
I'm not here for their war.

823
01:24:15.468 --> 01:24:18.429
I'm here for your life.

824
01:24:19.054 --> 01:24:21.098
You might be surprised.

825
01:24:21.182 --> 01:24:23.559
I'm not the same man you killed.

826
01:24:25.102 --> 01:24:27.605
I belong to the shadows now.

827
01:24:28.898 --> 01:24:30.983
And they belong to me.

828
01:24:48.667 --> 01:24:50.211
Looks like we're the main event.

829
01:24:50.920 --> 01:24:52.296
Let's kill this fucker.

830
01:25:03.849 --> 01:25:04.850
Just two more deaths

831
01:25:04.934 --> 01:25:06.894
and then Earthrealm belongs to me.

832
01:25:19.490 --> 01:25:20.490
Kano!

833
01:25:21.325 --> 01:25:24.119
Oi. where are you going?
This one's got the amulet.

834
01:25:52.147 --> 01:25:54.149
Vengeance will be mine.

835
01:26:12.918 --> 01:26:13.918
Kano!

836
01:26:17.172 --> 01:26:19.258
Now would be a good time
to use those powers. mate.

837
01:26:19.341 --> 01:26:20.467
What powers?

838
01:26:21.051 --> 01:26:22.891
Are you shitting me?
You don't have any powers?

839
01:26:23.637 --> 01:26:25.264
Just incredibly handsome.

840
01:26:25.347 --> 01:26:26.557
Oh. we're fucked.

841
01:26:30.686 --> 01:26:31.812
Grab it!

842
01:26:41.155 --> 01:26:42.197
I got it.

843
01:26:44.116 --> 01:26:45.492
How do we destroy it?

844
01:26:47.202 --> 01:26:48.746
Well fucked if I know.

845
01:26:48.829 --> 01:26:50.372
What do you mean you don't know?

846
01:26:50.456 --> 01:26:52.666
Mate. I found it for you.
Do I have to do everything?

847
01:26:53.250 --> 01:26:55.044
But this is your plan.

848
01:26:55.127 --> 01:26:56.187
Don't talk to me like that.

849
01:26:56.211 --> 01:26:58.171
Why don't you check the
instructions on the back?

850
01:26:58.213 --> 01:27:00.174
Oh. yeah. Yeah. that's a good idea.

851
01:27:00.257 --> 01:27:01.675
Oh. here we go. Look.

852
01:27:01.759 --> 01:27:03.218
One ring to rule them all.

853
01:27:03.302 --> 01:27:05.429
One ring to go fuck yourself!

854
01:27:05.512 --> 01:27:06.656
Why don't you leave the jokes to me?

855
01:27:06.680 --> 01:27:07.880
You can stick to being a cunt.

856
01:27:10.392 --> 01:27:11.392
Well. run!

857
01:27:46.303 --> 01:27:47.930
I am the one you want.

858
01:28:13.789 --> 01:28:15.290
Ah. fuck!

859
01:29:08.093 --> 01:29:09.970
I finally understand.

860
01:29:13.390 --> 01:29:16.018
Raiden told me I am not the chosen one.

861
01:29:16.101 --> 01:29:18.562
Your death belongs to another.

862
01:29:24.485 --> 01:29:27.196
My journey is to bring back Kung Lao.

863
01:29:28.072 --> 01:29:29.615
This is not the end.

864
01:29:31.909 --> 01:29:33.619
It is only the beginning.

865
01:29:51.386 --> 01:29:52.386
Fight.

866
01:29:55.557 --> 01:29:58.852
Congratulations. daughter. We just won.

867
01:30:00.813 --> 01:30:02.606
Earthrealm is ours.

868
01:30:08.862 --> 01:30:09.863
No.

869
01:30:11.907 --> 01:30:13.826
One fighter still remains.

870
01:30:22.251 --> 01:30:24.545
I renounce Outworld.

871
01:30:24.628 --> 01:30:28.090
I renounce your legacy of pain and cruelty.

872
01:30:28.674 --> 01:30:30.843
I renounce you!

873
01:30:33.846 --> 01:30:36.640
Today I fight for Earthrealm!

874
01:30:59.079 --> 01:31:00.497
So be it.

875
01:31:51.048 --> 01:31:52.174
The amulet.

876
01:32:06.230 --> 01:32:07.231
Never!

877
01:32:34.132 --> 01:32:35.467
Get over here!

878
01:33:56.715 --> 01:33:58.133
Hello. sunshine.

879
01:34:10.479 --> 01:34:13.106
With fire. be cleansed.

880
01:34:25.369 --> 01:34:27.120
<i>Johnny Cage.</i>

881
01:34:58.485 --> 01:35:00.779
<i>There are eight billion
people on this planet</i>

882
01:35:00.862 --> 01:35:02.948
<i>and yet the gods chose you.</i>

883
01:35:14.835 --> 01:35:16.711
You want to know my power?

884
01:35:17.671 --> 01:35:20.132
It doesn't have to end like this.

885
01:35:21.883 --> 01:35:23.885
You do not have to die.

886
01:35:26.179 --> 01:35:27.305
One of us does.

887
01:35:36.982 --> 01:35:38.817
For the first time in my life.

888
01:35:40.485 --> 01:35:43.280
I am Johnny fucking Cage.

889
01:36:15.353 --> 01:36:16.438
No.

890
01:36:17.314 --> 01:36:18.690
You should be dead.

891
01:36:19.566 --> 01:36:20.901
And you should be running.

892
01:36:44.633 --> 01:36:45.634
No.

893
01:37:55.787 --> 01:37:58.873
Weak. Just like your father.

894
01:38:13.388 --> 01:38:14.848
<i>Be strong. Kitana.</i>

895
01:38:36.786 --> 01:38:40.081
It's time for them to see you
for what you really are.

896
01:38:48.214 --> 01:38:49.549
Mortal.

897
01:39:12.238 --> 01:39:13.740
Stop. No.

898
01:39:15.408 --> 01:39:18.787
Please stand. Stand. Please.

899
01:39:26.044 --> 01:39:27.921
We are proud Edenians.

900
01:39:29.297 --> 01:39:31.174
We do not kneel.

901
01:39:37.681 --> 01:39:40.600
Kitana. our queen!

902
01:39:42.352 --> 01:39:45.772
Kitana. our queen!

903
01:39:46.564 --> 01:39:50.026
Kitana. our queen!

904
01:40:18.430 --> 01:40:20.223
<i>You want to know what makes a hero?</i>

905
01:40:25.103 --> 01:40:26.438
<i>It's not destiny.</i>

906
01:40:27.147 --> 01:40:28.857
<i>It's not something you're born with.</i>

907
01:40:31.317 --> 01:40:33.403
<i>It's discovering that sometimes</i>

908
01:40:33.486 --> 01:40:34.946
<i>even one small light</i>

909
01:40:35.029 --> 01:40:37.407
<i>is enough to hold back the darkness.</i>

910
01:40:39.117 --> 01:40:40.785
<i>It's facing unimaginable loss...</i>

911
01:40:43.455 --> 01:40:46.082
<i>and finding peace on the other side.</i>

912
01:40:55.300 --> 01:40:57.844
<i>It's lifting up the ones
you love. knowing...</i>

913
01:41:00.889 --> 01:41:04.392
<i>that they'll be there to
catch you when you fall.</i>

914
01:41:10.774 --> 01:41:12.609
<i>It's searching for greatness.</i>

915
01:41:15.069 --> 01:41:18.948
<i>then realizing you've had it
in you this entire time.</i>

916
01:41:20.867 --> 01:41:22.952
I say all of this to Raiden

917
01:41:23.036 --> 01:41:26.414
and he looks at me and he says...

918
01:41:27.123 --> 01:41:31.920
"You...
You have taught us so much. Mr. Cage.

919
01:41:32.921 --> 01:41:37.091
Thank you. Thank you
for sharing your wisdom."

920
01:41:38.051 --> 01:41:39.761
And you know what I tell him?

921
01:41:40.345 --> 01:41:41.596
What did you say?

922
01:41:42.138 --> 01:41:44.140
I said. "That ain't no wisdom. bub.

923
01:41:44.641 --> 01:41:47.310
That's perspective."

924
01:41:49.354 --> 01:41:52.524
Strange.
That is not how I remember it.

925
01:41:53.691 --> 01:41:55.026
Oh. Yo.

926
01:41:55.693 --> 01:41:57.445
I was just telling these guys

927
01:41:57.529 --> 01:42:00.198
how we saved all the realms. together.

928
01:42:00.281 --> 01:42:01.407
Oh.

929
01:42:01.908 --> 01:42:02.909
All right. Look...

930
01:42:03.660 --> 01:42:07.247
I may have taken one
or two creative liberties.

931
01:42:08.039 --> 01:42:09.040
Behold!

932
01:42:09.541 --> 01:42:12.919
The human female you rescued
from the pit of spikes.

933
01:42:13.795 --> 01:42:14.795
Seriously?

934
01:42:15.380 --> 01:42:17.131
Two or three creative liberties.

935
01:42:17.632 --> 01:42:18.818
You know. I've got to give it to you.

936
01:42:18.842 --> 01:42:20.602
I thought you'd go
running back to Hollywood

937
01:42:20.635 --> 01:42:21.636
first chance you got.

938
01:42:21.719 --> 01:42:23.888
I made a promise to these guys.

939
01:42:23.972 --> 01:42:25.515
Hollywood can wait.

940
01:42:27.600 --> 01:42:28.601
Oh. shit.

941
01:42:29.686 --> 01:42:31.080
Tell me there's not another tournament.

942
01:42:31.104 --> 01:42:33.273
No. Outworld has been defeated.

943
01:42:33.356 --> 01:42:34.524
Earthrealm has been saved.

944
01:42:35.692 --> 01:42:38.653
So. uh. what the fuck are you doing here?

945
01:42:38.736 --> 01:42:41.406
We have lost far too many of our champions.

946
01:42:41.489 --> 01:42:43.449
It's time to bring them home.

947
01:42:45.702 --> 01:42:47.412
Someone order a Necromancer?

948
01:42:47.996 --> 01:42:49.998
He might look like Voldemort's nut sack.

949
01:42:50.081 --> 01:42:52.417
but trust me. we're
going to need this fucker.

950
01:42:53.751 --> 01:42:57.088
Hey. g'day. Blondie. Long time no see.

951
01:42:58.339 --> 01:43:00.049
You ready for your next lesson?

952
01:43:00.133 --> 01:43:02.510
For the glory of Johnny Fucking Cage.

953
01:43:06.014 --> 01:43:08.683
Let's go get our friends.
Then we kill Kano.

954
01:43:10.852 --> 01:43:12.312
Yeah. Good.

954
